{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_13_03",
  "title": "鈴村優 3話 高い空に羽ばたこう",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――生徒会長選挙の一週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—One week before the student council election",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "二人で作ったポスターは……好評やし……\n毎日のあいさつ運動も、みんな返してくれるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The posters we made together… are getting good feedback…\nAnd everyone’s been responding to our daily greetings too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.5999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、朝も昼も、うちに付き合ってくれて\nへとへとやろ……ごめんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ you’ve been with me morning and noon‚\nyou must be exhausted… sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.8333332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "謝らないでちょうだい、ライブの準備も順調だし……\n優こそ……無理し過ぎちゃダメよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t apologize. The live preparations are going well too…\nYou’re the one who shouldn’t overdo it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9975474932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1081404209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……優はいろんな生徒に話し掛けられるように\nなったわね、目に見える成果が出ていて凄いわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… More and more students are starting to come up and talk to you‚\nand it’s amazing to see such clear results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8041492621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちのとこに、いろんな悩みを話しに来てくれる\nようにもなったんよ。ほんまに嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "People have started coming to me with all kinds of concerns‚\nand it makes me really happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9041493098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.6041512966
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "「困りごと、相談ごと、鈴村優になんでもお聞かせ\n下さい」って呼び掛けた効果ね。でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Any problems or concerns‚ please tell Yu Suzumura anything‚”\nthat campaign line is working. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.927575318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "疲れた～～～～…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So tired～～～～…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.927575318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6301587899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……行きましょうか、バスが来ちゃうわ\n今日は撮影の後はオフだし、寮でゆっくりしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Shall we go? The bus is coming.\nAfter the shoot today we’re off‚ so let’s relax at the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5904307842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "せやね、一旦休まんと……\n選挙もライブも息切れしてまうわ……ふわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we should take a break…\nOtherwise we’ll burn out before the election and the live… yawn",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2279307127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.8404307842
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.8404307842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "優、大丈夫？\nバスが来たわよ。すぐ乗れそうだし、頑張って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ are you okay?\nThe bus is here. Looks like we can get on right away‚ hang in there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8983898322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、お母さんみたいや……\nうち、寝たりせぇへん……大丈夫やで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ you sound like a mom…\nI won’t fall asleep… I’m fine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3983898799,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bus-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6166.666666600008,
          "startTime": 91.5650565465
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、優……そういえば、生徒会長を目指す理由は\n言葉になった？　そろそろ、教えてくれると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Yu… by the way‚ the reason you’re aiming to be president—\nhave you put it into words yet? It’d be nice if you could tell me soon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "すぅ……すぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Zzz… Zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.10555377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "寝てる……\nよっぽど疲れていたのね。ずっと一生懸命だったもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s asleep…\nShe must’ve been really exhausted. She’s been working so hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7666631062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "優、私ね、あなたのおかげで……\n学校でも、こんなに一生懸命になれて、嬉しいの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ because of you…\nI’ve been able to try this hard at school too… and it makes me happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7333262125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "優はいつも、私を支えてくれて……\nそれだけじゃなくて……新しい世界も見せてくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You always support me…\nand not just that… you’ve shown me a whole new world…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ふぁ……ダメ、バスの揺れが心地良くて……\n…………すぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yawn… no‚ the bus is rocking me to sleep…\n……Zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0333328246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――生徒会長選挙、候補者演説",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Student Council Election‚ Candidate Speeches",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0821078139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.8154406863
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.8154406863
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.9999994913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ次が、優の演説の番よ\nこの後は投票を残すのみ……ここが決めどころね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s finally your turn to give your speech‚ Yu.\nAfter this‚ only the vote remains… this is the decisive moment!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9999994913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.5083839574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "……うちの演説な、瑠依ちゃんに一番聞いてほしいんよ\nせやから、ここで――うちの一番近くで聞いてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I want you to hear my speech more than anyone‚ Rui-chan.\nSo—will you listen from right here‚ closest to me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.5083885827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.875050624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんよ、あなたから目を離したりしないわ\n一言も、聞き逃さないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. I won’t take my eyes off you.\nI won’t miss a single word.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.8666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.055979967
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ほな行ってきます\nうちの想い、みんなにぶつけてくるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I’m off.\nI’ll pour my feelings out to everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.1559845923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 179.722651259
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 179.722651259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "芸能コース一年の鈴村優といいます\nうちは生徒会長に立候補して、今ここに立っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Yu Suzumura‚ a first-year in the performing arts course.\nI’m standing here as a candidate for student council president.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.2893179256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 190.6226395129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "立候補した理由は、この学校の先輩でもある親友が\n『学校の意味』に疑問を持っていたことがきっかけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason I decided to run is because a close friend of mine‚\nwho is also a senior at this school‚ questioned the meaning of school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.422651259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.4559774716
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.4559774716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "え……優、それって……以前、私が聞いたこと……？\n学校に通うより、やるべきことがあるんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… Yu‚ is that… what I asked before…?\nThat maybe there are things more important than going to school…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.5666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.5568274656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにも、メッセや電話で\n相談したりして……でも、随分前のことなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You even messaged and called {user}-san about it…\nasking for advice… but that was so long ago…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.1666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 221.440067164
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 221.440067164
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "うちは学校の意味を疑ったこともなかったんです\nなんとなく必要やと思っていたし、当然通いたかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had never once questioned the meaning of school.\nI just thought it was something necessary‚ and of course I wanted to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.87339948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 232.0400554179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そうじゃない人もいる。意味があるのかって\n悩む人もいる。その悩みに、うちは向き合いたかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But not everyone feels that way. Some people struggle with\nwhether it really has any meaning. I wanted to face that struggle head-on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.27339948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 241.9067220846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "うち、学生時代は特別なものやと思うんです\nだって学生でいられるのは、たった数年だけなのに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe student life is something special.\nBecause you’re only a student for a few short years—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.5400661467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "大勢の漫画家さんが題材にしたり、多くの作品が\n生み出されて。沢山の人が観て、読んで、共感して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "yet so many manga artists use it as a theme‚ and countless works\nare created from it—so many people watch‚ read‚ and relate…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.0400661467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 260.2400554179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "そんな特別な時間は、人生の中でそうあるもんやない\nだからうちは、学年も、コースも関係なく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Time that special doesn’t come often in life.\nThat’s why‚ regardless of grade or course…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.8400661467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "生徒みんなに、漫画みたいな、輝く青春を送ってほしい\n無駄じゃない、通って良かったって思える場所にしたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want every student to experience a shining youth‚ like in manga.\nI want to make this a place where you feel it wasn’t a waste—where you’re glad you came.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.2400661467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 281.0400472799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "その親友に聞かれた時には、答えられへんかったけど\n学校に、そんな意味を持たせたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn’t answer my friend back then‚\nbut I want to give school that kind of meaning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.6400580087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "そのために、うちが生徒会長になったら\n誰でも、なんでも話を聞かせてほしいと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And for that‚ if I become student council president‚\nI want everyone to feel free to tell me anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.6400580087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 297.2400472799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "友達にはちょっと話しにくいとか、相談しにくいとか\n誰に話していいか分からん時、うちに話してほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things that are hard to tell friends‚ or hard to talk about—\nwhen you don’t know who to turn to‚ I want you to come to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 302.0067246753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "あなたの学校生活の主人公は、あなたなんです\nあなたが輝くためのお手伝いをさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are the protagonist of your own school life.\nPlease let me help you shine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 311.2400580087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 314.9400472799
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 319.8400580087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "どうか、うち、鈴村優をよろしくお願いします\n会長になったら、生徒会室で待ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please support me‚ Yu Suzumura.\nIf I become president‚ I’ll be waiting in the student council room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.8400580087,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
          "delay": 9959.933853300015,
          "startTime": 329.799991862
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
          "delay": 10059.933853299981,
          "startTime": 329.899991862
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "聞いて下さり、ありがとうございました\n芸能コース一年、鈴村優",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much for listening.\nFirst-year performing arts course‚ Yu Suzumura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.1067246753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Live Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 332.3400452454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
