      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 335.2433190919
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 336.8067546368
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 340.8734381358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの準備も間に合ってほんまに良かった～！\n終わったらすみれちゃん、うんと労わなあかんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so glad we made it in time for the live!\nAfter this‚ we really need to treat Sumire well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 340.8734381358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 345.1734213035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、優の『生徒会長当選』のお祝いも\n一緒にやりましょう。ね、異例の一年生生徒会長さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ let’s celebrate your election as president too—\nour unprecedented first-year president.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 348.2000137329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 349.8666585286
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 353.5409947237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、おおきにやで。でも、それを言うたら\n瑠依ちゃんの支えがあったからこそや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu‚ thanks. But if we’re saying that‚\nit’s only thanks to your support‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 358.8743448894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 362.0743280571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……このライブが終わったら、いつも通り\nトリエル三人で、お鍋で打ち上げしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then… once this live is over‚ as usual‚\nthe three of us in TRINITYAiLE can celebrate with hot pot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 365.3733072176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 369.0302918276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "うん、それがええなぁ！\nそろそろ開演やね。ほな、行こか、瑠依ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that sounds perfect!\nIt’s about time. Let’s go‚ Rui-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 372.2969753266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 376.9302918276
    },
    {
